### **Issue 9: 구현 흔들림 - 간단한 Base64/Encryption**

**위치**: `src/security/auth.rs` 라인 169-198

**문제점**:
```rust
fn base64_encode(data: &str) -> String {
    let bytes = data.as_bytes();
    let mut result = String::new();

    for &byte in bytes {
        result.push_str(&format!("{:02x}", byte));  // ← Hex, 실제 Base64 아님!
    }

    result
}

fn base64_decode(encoded: &str) -> Result<String, String> {
    // Hex 디코딩, 실제 Base64 아님
